dc_title_s: Parcels Fond du Lac County, WI 2011
dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents tax parcels for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2011.[The Parcels layer depicts tax parcels within Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin. It has a variety of sources such as deed descriptions, subdivision plats, and certified survey maps. The County Land Information Department maintains these files.This data is current through December 31, 2011.Publication Date: January 24, 2012.]
